{"tid":2395562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬：英超太多「埋身肉搏」嚇親我","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T05:01:29.000Z","uid":31314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0012f5f33ed9fe63b896a0aa46f0c3ab7d28e3","tid":2395562,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"尼馬指英超風格太多身體接觸，是他沒有選擇到英超發展的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬（Neymar）接受英國《每日郵報》訪問時，稱自己被英超嚇得卻步的箇中原因：「我沒有看過太多英超比賽，但我經常聽聞在比賽中有很多身體接觸。當然法甲都有！」他更指出2020似乎打破了不少人的希望與打算，所以他更為珍惜自己擁有的一切，希望全力為PSG奪下歐聯，更想為巴西取得世界盃。 尼馬在場上不時成為敵方球員追擊的目標，更曾因此而多次受傷，難免抗拒粗野踢法。有報道指，29歲的尼馬除了沒有打算轉戰英超，更已準備好長線留在法甲發展，有望跟巴黎聖日耳門續簽4年新約。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/da33539b7c64baf4ae8d4fd7a5ee2850/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fda33539b7c64baf4ae8d4fd7a5ee2850%2Ftenor.gif&h=8f1905bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d18ufwot1963hr.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03122439/ball.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd18ufwot1963hr.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F03122439%2Fball.gif&h=92742c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/6b/2a/2b/6b2a2b689c041169dbc653cdf4ea98ff.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F6b%2F2a%2F2b%2F6b2a2b689c041169dbc653cdf4ea98ff.gif&h=988295db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180706/e3f97b08b6de48219f15e3a56afdb42b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180706%2Fe3f97b08b6de48219f15e3a56afdb42b.gif&h=74ca9aa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cb5ec258db1a6f9632a46a193295a2f1a1b4654","tid":2395562,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"以前踢學界都好憎比人掂到, 啲汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266ec2fcb33